---
title: BBQ Glazed Tofu Steaks with Corn Cobs, Slaw & Wedges
description: We’re using the American definition of BBQ for this recipe, referring to the rich and smokey sauce that covers the tofu as it bakes. Add some golden wedges, baked corn cobs and crisp slaw for a tried and true taste of the USA!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5de83210319de564d36c7094-24ff0bf1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/bbq-glazed-tofu-steaks-5de83210319de564d36c7094-89f0bb1c.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/bbq-glazed-tofu-steaks-5de83210319de564d36c7094
author: HelloFresh
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 3360 kcal
